    "default": "require challenge.md, notes.md, closeout_record, extraction_output, passing closeout validation, and no active discrepancy carrying no_closeout; require solution and recap.md when outcome is solved, require recap.md but not solution when outcome is blocked_closeout or unresolved, and allow omission of both only for closed_without_attempt",
